control_light_activity::clip_card_0::goa: Kofakee yookaan mul'ina ifaakee jijjiiruudhaan ifa tu'achuu shaakali.
control_light_activity::text_card_1::tex: Bu'uura Suuraa Bilbilaa xumuruukeef baga gammadde! Suuraakee #StoryMaker jettee iyyaatessuun hawaasa StoryMaker'iif hiruu hin irraanfatin.
control_light_activity::title: Sochii Ifaa tu'adhu
control_light_activity::text_card_0::tex: Amma erga barumsa ifa hoogganuu barattee, kutaan kun akka ati shaakaltuuf si gargaara.
control_light_activity::text_card_2::tex: Qabduu duuba jedhu kan sajoo StoryMaker'itti aanee argii gara oliitti argamu tuquudhaan manatti deebi'uu dandeessa.
